      "value": "<p>Through long and intensive training you mastered Shrouded Subterfuge. Few people in this world can match your capabilities in this area.</p><p>Gain the following master feats: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.u96anl3ACNhBqnbT]{Go with the Flow}.</p><p><strong>Skill Potency</strong></p><p>At 9th level, you gain a +2 item bonus to Occultism checks involving @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.AJstokjdG6iDjVjE]{Impersonate}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.ewwCglB7XOPLUz72]{Lie}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.plBGdZhqq5JBl1D8]{Gather Information}. At 17th level, this bonus increases to +3.</p>",
